<dd> <a href="http://www.handle.net">Sam Sun</a>, CNRI, 
     <em>Handle System Namespace and its Service Definition</em>
<p>
Each presentation will be approximately 30 minutes long with 15 minutes
for Q/A (total 45 minutes each). 
